---

## Design principles

- **Local-first** ‚Äî SQLite by default; no cloud dependency.
- **Modular** ‚Äî each module has clean boundaries and can be used independently.
- **Extensible** ‚Äî adapters, operators, scorers, and test types are all plug-in.
- **Production-grade structure** ‚Äî suitable for CI/CD gating and lightweight production monitoring.
- **No auth in v1** ‚Äî token-based access; pluggable auth layer is a planned v2 addition.

